 roadshow, the company sensitised Nigerians on the product knowledge and the Pay Per View and A La Carte concepts of the brand. Below are some of the images from the roadshow, as it went down: <img class="aligncenter wp-image-1470167" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=603%2C402&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="603" height="402" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C683&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=58%2C39&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=260%2C173&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=195%2C130&amp;ssl=1 195w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?resize=115%2C77&amp;ssl=1 115w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_4123-scaled.jpg?w=1920&amp;ssl=1 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 603px) 100vw, 603px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-1470169" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/DSC_3850-scaled.jpg?resize=606%2C404&